    <comment>soapy-uhd: fix the build against UHD 4.x (C++17, needed by UHD's std::optional/std::is_convertible_v headers) and recent Boost (explicit boost/lexical_cast.hpp include), rescuing it from the botdel (SR 1360107). No version change (already at latest). Both fixes submitted upstream: pothosware/SoapyUHD#75 and #76.</comment>
